data.description: Welcome to your dream townhome in the heart of a picturesque community! This stunning three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom townhome offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Nestled within a gated community, relish in the tranquility and security provided, while still being conveniently close to major amenities.This residence boasts a modern layout with spacious living areas, ideal for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet evenings. The well-equipped kitchen features sleek appliances, ample storage.
